After constant rumours of a snag in the marriage between IK Ogbonna and Sonia Morales, the union has finally crashed.  Sonia Morales, who is a South American took to her social media account to announce that she has parted ways with model and actor IK Ogbonna. Her announcement has elicited reactions on social media with some celebrity single mothers commending her for her bold step. The significant parties are actors Tonto Dikeh and Yvonne Jegede whose marriages failed after producing a child each. IK Ogbonna has been silent on social media since Sonia who has been holidaying around the world posting sultry pictures made the announcement.  Source